-- =*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=
-- Author:		Vincent D'Souza
-- Create date: February 13, 2023
-- Description:	Returns TRUE (1) or FALSE (0) based on the CallNumber exist for an Account Code AND AllowDuplicateCallNumber flag
-- =*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].udf_IsCallNumberExistForAccountCode
	( @AccountCodeId INT
	, @CallNumber VARCHAR(255)
	) 
RETURNS BIT
AS
	BEGIN
		DECLARE @IsDuplicateCallNumberAllowed INT

		SELECT @IsDuplicateCallNumberAllowed = COUNT(CallNumber)
			FROM  [ETPS2_APD].CM_Calls WITH (NOLOCK) 
		WHERE CallNumber = @CallNumber 
			AND AccountCodeID_FK = @AccountCodeID
			AND AllowDuplicateCallNumber = 0

		RETURN IIF(@IsDuplicateCallNumberAllowed > 1, 1, 0)
	END
function.name: udf_IsCallNumberExistForAccountCode

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].AU_RepDocuSignInfobyRepIdESignatureUserGet
  @username varchar(50) 
/***************************************************************************
OBJECT NAME			: dbo.AU_RepDocuSignInfobyRepIdESignatureUserGet
CALLING PROGRAM		: Rep Service 
INPUT PARAMETERS        : @username varchar(50)
OUTPUT PARAMETER        : NONE
CALLING SYNTAX		: exec  dbo.AU_RepDocuSignInfobyRepIdESignatureUserGet
DESCRIPTION			: return top 1 rep id, email address and docusignid with ActiveFlag 
                      equal 1 and StatusId equal 2
TIBCO PROCESS		:   
TIBCO SUB PROCESS	: 
MODIFICATION HISTORY:
=============================================================================
DATE		VERSION		MODIFIED BY		DESCRIPTION
=============================================================================
07/08/2022	1.0.0		Eva Adamovich		Initial Creation: MWOMSS-352
07/15/2022	1.0.1		Eva Adamovich		Initial Creation: MWOMSS-352 mistake found in the original spreadsheet
--and es.StatusId = 2   and ui.username = @username line was commented
****************************************************************************/
AS
BEGIN
 SET NOCOUNT ON;
 
		Select top 1 ui.RepId, es.EmailAddress as DocuSignEmailAddress, es.DocuSignId 
		From Auth.dbo.UserInfo ui
			inner join Auth.dbo.ESignatureUser es 
			 on ui.UserId = es.UserInfoId
		where  ui.ActiveFlag = 1 and es.StatusId = 2 
                and ui.username = @username 
 End
GRANT EXECUTE ON  dbo.AU_RepDocuSignInfobyRepIdESignatureUserGet TO PUBLIC
storedProcedure.name: AU_RepDocuSignInfobyRepIdESignatureUserGet

CREATE   PROCEDURE [dbo].[CWT_getAccountsbysearch]
	@reps varchar(max),
	@accountTypes int,
	@noHouseholdMembers bit = 0,
	@accountNo varchar(20) = NULL,
	@accountName varchar(40) = NULL,
	@groupName varchar(40) = NULL,
	@ssnTaxID varchar(9) = NULL,
	@minAccountValue money = NULL,
	@maxAccountValue money = NULL,
	@accountClasses varchar(200) = NULL,
	@investmentObjectives varchar(32) = NULL,
	@includeZeroBalance bit = 0,
-- Sorting arguments
	@firstSortField varchar(40)  = NULL,
	@firstSortOrder bit = NULL,
	@thenSortField varchar(40) = NULL,
	@thenSortOrder bit = NULL,
	@PageNumber INT = 1,  
	@PageSize INT = 500,
-- For debugging only
	@debug bit = 0
AS

    SET NOCOUNT ON;
--==============================================================================
	--Unit Tests:

 --exec CWT_getAccountsBySearch @reps=N'(''90MA'')',
    --@accountTypes=3,@includeZeroBalance=0,@accountNo=default,@accountName=N'',@groupName=default,@ssnTaxID=default,
	--@firstSortField=N'AccountName',@firstSortOrder=0,@debug=1

--********************************************************************************************
DECLARE @sql					nvarchar(MAX)
DECLARE @sqlSelect				nvarchar(max)
DECLARE @sqlWhere				nvarchar(max)
DECLARE @sqlOrderBy				nvarchar(400)
DECLARE @sqlTempSelect			nvarchar(max)
DECLARE @sqlSelectPart2			nvarchar(max)
DECLARE @accountsColumns        nvarchar(max)
DECLARE @sqlLastStatement		nvarchar(400)
DECLARE @accountLocs			nvarchar(400)
DECLARE @FirstRow				INT    
  
DECLARE @LastRow				INT  
DECLARE @INT_MAX				INT  
  
SET @INT_MAX = 2147483647

IF OBJECT_ID('tempdb..#temp') IS NOT NULL
	TRUNCATE TABLE #temp
ELSE
	CREATE TABLE #temp (
	RowNum int
	,AccountId int	
	,AccountLocationCode int
	,RepId char(4)
	,LPLAccountNo char(8)
	,SponsorAccountNo varchar(20)
	,SponsorCode varchar(4)
	,SponsorType char(1)
	,Cusip char(9)
	,SecurityId int
	,SecuritySourceCode int
	,SSNTaxId varchar(9)
	,IsSSN tinyint
	,AccountName varchar(40)
	,IsClosed tinyint
	,IsThirdParty tinyint
	,AccountClassCode varchar(4)
	,AccountTitle varchar(120)
	,InvestmentObjectiveCode char(2)
	,CombStmt varchar(7)
	,ProductName varchar(30)
	,TotalAccountValue money
	,LPLAccountValue money
	,OutsideAccountValue money
	,AsOfDate datetime
	,TransferStatus char(1)
	,HomePhone char(11)
	,AccountOpenDate datetime
	,AccountClosedDate datetime
	,Suppress tinyint
	,NetworkedLPLAccountID int
	,PrimaryBirthDate datetime
	,ResidencyStatesCodes varchar(128)
	,IsMMDAEligible tinyint
	,AdvisorFeePercent float
	,AdvisoryFeeCycle tinyint
	,IsMMDAGroupable tinyint
	,[Type] char(3)
	,AccountValue money
	,NetworkedAccountValue money
	,ClientGroupID int
	,ClientGroupName varchar(80)
	,HHGroupID int
	,HHGroupName varchar(80)
	,CSGroupID int
	,CSGroupName varchar(80)
	,ICAGroupID int
	,ICAGroupName varchar(80)
	,ASGroupID int
	,ASGroupName varchar(80)
	,ASExemption int
	,ASNickname varchar(15)
	,IsICAGroupEligible bit
	,IsCSGroupEligible bit
	,Exemption int
	,ASEligible tinyint
	,NoNames tinyint
	,Name1 varchar(30)
	,Name2 varchar(30)
	,Name3 varchar(30)
	,Name4 varchar(30)
	,Name5 varchar(30)
	,Name6 varchar(30)
	,AccountClassName varchar(10)
	,InvestmentObjective varchar(50)
	)

SELECT @firstRow = 1, @lastRow = @INT_MAX  
  
 IF @pageSize <> @INT_MAX AND @pageNumber > 0  
 BEGIN  
  SET @firstRow = ( @pageSize * ( @pageNumber - 1 ) ) + 1  
  SET @lastRow = @pageSize * @pageNumber  
 END

-- Begin WHERE clause --
SET @sqlWhere = ''
SET @accountLocs = '0'

IF ( (@accountTypes & 1) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',1'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 2) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',2'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 4) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',4'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 8) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',8'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 16) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',16'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 32) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',32'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 64) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',64'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 128) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',128'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 0x100) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',0x100'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 0x200) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',0x200'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 0x400) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',0x400'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 0x800) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',0x800'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 0x1000) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',0x1000'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 0x2000) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',0x2000'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 0x4000) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',0x4000'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 0x10000) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',0x10000'
IF ( (@accountTypes & 0x20000) > 0 ) SET @accountLocs = @accountLocs + ',0x20000'
	
	-- Filter out records that have the Suppress flag set
SET @sqlWhere = '(lplca.Suppress IS NULL OR lplca.Suppress = 0) AND '
	
	-- Unless otherwise specified, filter out Direct Business accounts that have a zero balance
	-- Note: Do not apply the zero-balance check against LPL or Unofficial accounts - only Direct Business accounts
IF @includeZeroBalance = 0
BEGIN
	SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + '(CASE WHEN lplca.AccountLocationCode NOT IN (1, 2, 16) THEN lplca.TotalAccountValue ELSE 1 END) > 0 AND '
END
	
-- @reps and @accountTypes are required
SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + 'lplca.RepID IN ' + @reps + ' AND ( lplca.AccountLocationCode IN (' + @accountLocs + ') )'
	
IF ( @accountTypes & 1 > 0 )
BEGIN
	-- Check for @accountClasses
	IF @accountClasses IS NOT NULL
	BEGIN
		SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' AND AccountClassCode IN ' + @accountClasses
	END
		
	-- Check for @investmentObjectives
	IF @investmentObjectives IS NOT NULL
	BEGIN
		SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + 'AND InvestmentObjectiveCode IN ' + @investmentObjectives
	END
END
	
	-- Check for @accountName
IF @accountName IS NOT NULL
BEGIN
	IF @accountName = '#'
	BEGIN
		SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' AND AccountName > ''0'' AND AccountName < ''A'''
	END
	-- Search for accounts beginning with literal string
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' AND AccountName LIKE @accountName + ''%'' ESCAPE ''~'''
	END		
END

-- Check for @groupName
IF @groupName IS NOT NULL
BEGIN
	SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' AND (ClientGroupName LIKE @groupName + ''%'' ESCAPE ''~'' OR HHGroupName LIKE @groupName + ''%'' ESCAPE ''~'' OR CSGroupName LIKE @groupName + ''%'' ESCAPE ''~'' OR ICAGroupName LIKE @groupName + ''%'' ESCAPE ''~'')'
END
	
-- Check for @ssnTaxID
IF @ssnTaxID IS NOT NULL
BEGIN
	SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' AND lplca.SSNTaxID LIKE @ssnTaxID + ''%'''
END

-- Check for @minAccountValue
IF @minAccountValue IS NOT NULL
BEGIN
	SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' AND lplca.TotalAccountValue >= @minAccountValue'
END
-- Check for @maxAccountValue
IF @maxAccountValue IS NOT NULL
BEGIN
	SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' AND lplca.TotalAccountValue <= @maxAccountValue'
END
	-- Check for @AccountNo
IF @accountNo IS NOT NULL
BEGIN
	Set @accountNo = LTRIM(RTRIM(@accountNo))
	SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' AND ('
		
	IF (@accountTypes & 1) > 0
	BEGIN
		SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + 'LPLAccountNo LIKE @accountNo + ''%'''
	END
		
	IF ( @accountTypes & 4 > 0 ) OR ( @accountTypes & 8 > 0 ) OR ( @accountTypes & 16 > 0 ) OR ( @accountTypes & 64 > 0 )
	BEGIN
		IF (@accountTypes & 1) > 0
		BEGIN
			SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' OR '
		END
			
		SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + 'SponsorAccountNo LIKE @accountNo + ''%'''
	END
		
	SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ')'
END
-- Check @noHouseholdMembers
IF @noHouseholdMembers = 1
BEGIN
	SET @sqlWhere = @sqlWhere + ' AND ag.HHGroupID IS NULL '
END
IF LEN( @sqlWhere ) > 0
BEGIN
	SET @sqlWhere = ' WHERE ' + @sqlWhere
END
-- End WHERE clause --

-- Begin ORDER BY string
SET @sqlOrderBy = ''
-- Check for @firstSortField
IF @firstSortField IS NOT NULL
	BEGIN
		IF @firstSortField = 'RepID'
		BEGIN
			SET @firstSortField = 'lplca.RepID'
		END
		SET @sqlOrderBy = @sqlOrderBy + @firstSortField
		-- If  @firstSortOrder is supplied and is not 0 (Ascending), append DESC (if 1, ASC is implied)
		IF @firstSortOrder IS NOT NULL
		BEGIN
			IF @firstSortOrder = 1
			BEGIN
				SET @sqlOrderBy = @sqlOrderBy + ' DESC'
			END
		END
	END
	
	-- Check for @thenSortField
IF @thenSortField IS NOT NULL
	BEGIN
		--HACK: Fix ambiguous column reference...
		IF @thenSortField = 'RepID'
		BEGIN
			SET @thenSortField = 'lplca.RepID'
		END
	
		-- Append comma if more than one sort field
		IF LEN(@sqlOrderBy) > 0
		BEGIN
			SET @sqlOrderBy = @sqlOrderBy + ', '
		END
	
		-- Append field name
		SET @sqlOrderBy = @sqlOrderBy + @thenSortField
	
		-- If  @thenSortOrder is supplied and is not 0 (Ascending), append DESC (if 1, ASC is implied)
		IF @thenSortOrder IS NOT NULL
		BEGIN
			IF @thenSortOrder = 1
			BEGIN
				SET @sqlOrderBy = @sqlOrderBy + ' DESC'
			END

		END
	END
	
	-- Prepend 'ORDER BY' before field names
IF LEN(@sqlOrderBy) > 0
	BEGIN
		SET @sqlOrderBy = ' ORDER BY ' + @sqlOrderBy
	END

-- End ORDER BY string

	-- SELECT list for "Existing LPL Accounts" SQL
	-- NOTE:  The extra aliased columns are for existing application support - may be removed eventually

SET @accountsColumns = 'lplca.AccountId,lplca.AccountLocationCode,lplca.RepId,lplca.LPLAccountNo,lplca.SponsorAccountNo,'+
		'lplca.SponsorCode,lplca.SponsorType,lplca.Cusip,'+
		'lplca.SecurityId,lplca.SecuritySourceCode,lplca.SSNTaxId,lplca.IsSSN,'+
		'lplca.AccountName,lplca.IsClosed,lplca.IsThirdParty,lplca.AccountClassCode,lplca.AccountTitle,'+
		'lplca.InvestmentObjectiveCode,lplca.CombStmt,lplca.ProductName,lplca.TotalAccountValue,'+
		'lplca.LPLAccountValue,lplca.OutsideAccountValue,lplca.AsOfDate,'+
		'lplca.TransferStatus,lplca.HomePhone,lplca.AccountOpenDate,lplca.AccountClosedDate,'+
		'lplca.Suppress,lplca.NetworkedLPLAccountID,lplca.PrimaryBirthDate,lplca.ResidencyStatesCodes,'+
		'lplca.IsMMDAEligible,lplca.AdvisorFeePercent,lplca.AdvisoryFeeCycle,lplca.IsMMDAGroupable';
-- LPL
SET @sqlSelect = 'INSERT INTO #temp ' +
        'SELECT RowNum, AccountId, AccountLocationCode, RepId, LPLAccountNo, SponsorAccountNo, SponsorCode, ' +
        'SponsorType, Cusip, SecurityId, SecuritySourceCode, SSNTaxId, IsSSN, AccountName, IsClosed, ' +
        'IsThirdParty, AccountClassCode, AccountTitle, InvestmentObjectiveCode, CombStmt, ProductName, ' +
        'TotalAccountValue, LPLAccountValue, OutsideAccountValue, AsOfDate, TransferStatus, HomePhone, ' +
        'AccountOpenDate, AccountClosedDate, Suppress, NetworkedLPLAccountID, PrimaryBirthDate, ResidencyStatesCodes, ' +
        'IsMMDAEligible, AdvisorFeePercent, AdvisoryFeeCycle, IsMMDAGroupable, Type, AccountValue, NetworkedAccountValue, ' +
        'ClientGroupID, ClientGroupName, HHGroupID, HHGroupName, CSGroupID, CSGroupName, ICAGroupID, ICAGroupName, ' +
        'ASGroupID, ASGroupName, ASExemption, ASNickname, IsICAGroupEligible, IsCSGroupEligible, Exemption, ASEligible, ' +
        'NoNames, Name1, Name2, Name3, Name4, Name5, Name6, AccountClassName, InvestmentObjective ' +
        'FROM (SELECT TOP 2147483647 ROW_NUMBER() OVER(' + @sqlOrderBy + ') AS RowNum, ';
SET @sqlSelectPart2 = ', loc.AccountLocationShortName AS Type, ' +
        '(CASE WHEN lplca.AccountLocationCode IN (1,2) THEN lplca.LPLAccountValue ELSE lplca.TotalAccountValue END) AS AccountValue, ' +
        '(CASE WHEN lplca.AccountLocationCode = 16 THEN NULL ELSE lplca.OutsideAccountValue END) AS NetworkedAccountValue, ' +
        'ag.ClientGroupID, ag.ClientGroupName, ' +
        'ag.HHGroupID, ag.HHGroupName, ' +
        'ag.CSGroupID, ag.CSGroupName, ' +
        'ag.ICAGroupID, ag.ICAGroupName, ' +
        'ag.ASGroupID, ag.ASGroupName, ag.ASExemption, ' +
        'am.ASNickname, ' +
        '(CASE WHEN lplca.IsMMDAEligible = 1 OR lplca.IsMMDAGroupable = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS IsICAGroupEligible, ' +
        '(CASE WHEN lplca.AccountLocationCode IN (1,2) THEN Support.dbo.IsCSEligible(lplca.LPLAccountNo) ELSE 0 END) AS IsCSGroupEligible, ' +
        'gi.Exemption, ' +
        'acs.ASEligible, ' +
        'bam.NoNames, bam.Name1, bam.Name2, bam.Name3, bam.Name4, bam.Name5, bam.Name6, ' +
        'acs.ShortName AS AccountClassName, inv.AbbreviatedDesc AS InvestmentObjective ' +
        'FROM LPLCustomer.dbo.Account lplca WITH (NOLOCK) ' +
        'INNER JOIN LPLCustomer.dbo.AccountLocation loc WITH (NOLOCK) ON lplca.AccountLocationCode = loc.AccountLocationCode ' +
        'LEFT OUTER JOIN PortfolioManager.dbo.AccountGroups_ById ag WITH (NOLOCK) ON lplca.AccountId = ag.AccountId AND lplca.AccountLocationCode = ag.AccountLocationCode ' +
        'LEFT OUTER JOIN PortfolioManager.dbo.AccountMember am  WITH (NOLOCK) ON lplca.AccountID = am.AccountID AND (am.ASNickname IS NOT NULL AND am.ASNickname <> '''') ' +
        'LEFT OUTER JOIN PortfolioManager.dbo.GroupInfo gi  WITH (NOLOCK) ON am.GroupID = gi.GroupID AND gi.GroupType = 16 ' +
        'LEFT OUTER JOIN [BETA].[dbo].[CWT_VW_BetaAcctMstr_NewMaster] bam WITH (NOLOCK)  ON lplca.LPLAccountNo = bam.AccountNo ' +
        'LEFT OUTER JOIN SUPPORT.dbo.AccountClass acs WITH (NOLOCK)  ON lplca.AccountClassCode = acs.LPLCode AND acs.LPLCode = CASE ' +
        'WHEN acs.FirmID = 1 THEN ''001'' ' +
        'WHEN acs.FirmID = 14 THEN ''014'' ' +
        'ELSE ''007'' END ' +
        'LEFT OUTER JOIN SUPPORT.dbo.InvestmentObjective inv WITH (NOLOCK)  ON lplca.InvestmentObjectiveCode = inv.LPLCode ';

SET @sqlTempSelect = ') RSLT  select   RowNum, AccountId, AccountLocationCode, RepId, LPLAccountNo, SponsorAccountNo, 
		SponsorCode, SponsorType, Cusip, SecurityId, SecuritySourceCode, 
		SSNTaxId, IsSSN, AccountName, IsClosed, IsThirdParty, AccountClassCode, 
		AccountTitle, InvestmentObjectiveCode, CombStmt, ProductName, TotalAccountValue, 
		LPLAccountValue, OutsideAccountValue, AsOfDate, TransferStatus, HomePhone, AccountOpenDate, 
		AccountClosedDate, Suppress, NetworkedLPLAccountID, PrimaryBirthDate, ResidencyStatesCodes, 
		IsMMDAEligible, AdvisorFeePercent, AdvisoryFeeCycle, IsMMDAGroupable, Type, AccountValue, 
		NetworkedAccountValue, ClientGroupID,ClientGroupName, HHGroupID, HHGroupName, CSGroupID, CSGroupName, 
		ICAGroupID, ICAGroupName, ASGroupID, ASGroupName, ASExemption, ASNickname, IsICAGroupEligible, 
		IsCSGroupEligible, Exemption, ASEligible, NoNames, Name1, Name2, Name3, Name4, Name5, Name6, 
		AccountClassName, InvestmentObjective ';
SET @sqlLastStatement = ' from #temp  WHERE RowNum BETWEEN ' + STR(@firstRow) +' AND ' + STR(@lastRow ) + ' select count(1) As TotalCount from #temp';



SET @sql = cast(@sqlSelect as nvarchar(MAX)) + cast(@accountsColumns as nvarchar(MAX))+ cast(@sqlSelectPart2 as nvarchar(MAX))+cast(@sqlWhere as nvarchar(MAX)) + cast(@sqlOrderBy as nvarchar(MAX)) + --cast(@sqlResult as nvarchar(MAX))
			+ cast(@sqlTempSelect as nvarchar(MAX))+ cast(@sqlLastStatement as nvarchar(MAX))

IF @debug <> 0
BEGIN
	PRINT	CHAR(13) + CHAR(13) +
		'/* Begin DEBUG Output */' + CHAR(13) +
		@sqlSelect + CHAR(13) +
		CHAR(13) + CHAR(13) +
		@accountsColumns+ + CHAR(13) +
		CHAR(13) + CHAR(13) +
		@sqlSelectPart2+ + CHAR(13) +
		CHAR(13) + CHAR(13) +
		@sqlWhere +
		CHAR(13) + CHAR(13) +
		@sqlOrderBy+
		CHAR(13) + CHAR(13) +
		@sqlTempSelect+
		CHAR(13) + CHAR(13) +
		@sqlLastStatement+
		'/* End DEBUG Output */' + CHAR(13) +
		CHAR(13) + CHAR(13)
END

execute sp_executesql 	@sql,

			N'@accountNo varchar(20),
			@accountName varchar(40),
			@groupName varchar(40),
			@ssnTaxID varchar(9),
			@minAccountValue money,
			@maxAccountValue money',

			@accountNo,
			@accountName,
			@groupName,
			@ssnTaxID,
			@minAccountValue,
			@maxAccountValue
storedProcedure.name: CWT_getAccountsbysearch

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[usp_credit_ledger_insert] (
	@RepId VARCHAR(50) = NULL,
   @ContractId INT = NULL,
   @SubscriptionProductId INT = NULL,
   @ProductId INT = NULL,
   @PlanType VARCHAR(50) = NULL,
   @CreditBalance INT = NULL,
   @ContractStartDate DATETIME2 = NULL,
   @ContractEndDate DATETIME2 = NULL,
   @InsertType VARCHAR(50) = NULL
)
-- ===============================================================================
-- (c)2022 LPL Financial. All Rights Reserved.
-- Date: 2022-09-21
-- Author: Peter Avenarius
-- Summary: Inserts a new credit ledger
-- Example:
--    EXEC paraplanning.usp_credit_ledger_insert 'T2XA', 38628, 386, None, 0, '2022-08-30 00:00:00.0000000', '2023-02-28 00:00:00.0000000'
-- ===============================================================================
AS
BEGIN
	SET NOCOUNT ON;

   DECLARE @InsertLog table(
      [id] [INT] NOT NULL,
      [rep_id] [VARCHAR](50) NULL,
	   [sf_contract_id] [INT] NULL,
      [sf_subscription_product_id] [INT] NOT NULL,
      [sf_product_id] [INT] NOT NULL,
	   [plan_type] [VARCHAR](50) NULL,
	   [credit_balance] [INT] NULL,
      [contract_start_date] [DATETIME2] NULL,
      [contract_end_date] [DATETIME2] NULL,
	   [created_date] [DATETIME2] NULL,
	   [last_updated] [DATETIME2] NULL
      );

   DECLARE @CurrentDateTime DATETIME2 = SYSDATETIME();
   DECLARE @InsertSubscriptionProductId INT = NULL
   IF (@SubscriptionProductId IS NOT NULL)
      BEGIN
         SET @InsertSubscriptionProductId = @SubscriptionProductId
      END
   ELSE
      BEGIN
         SET @InsertSubscriptionProductId = @ProductId
      END

	INSERT INTO dbo.credit_ledger(rep_id, sf_contract_id, sf_subscription_product_id, sf_product_id, plan_type, credit_balance,
      contract_start_date, contract_end_date, created_date, last_updated)
   OUTPUT INSERTED.id, INSERTED.rep_id, INSERTED.sf_contract_id, INSERTED.sf_subscription_product_id, INSERTED.sf_product_id, INSERTED.plan_type, INSERTED.credit_balance,
      INSERTED.contract_start_date, INSERTED.contract_end_date, INSERTED.created_date, INSERTED.last_updated
   INTO @InsertLog
   VALUES(@RepId, @ContractId, @InsertSubscriptionProductId, @ProductId, @PlanType, @CreditBalance, @ContractStartDate, @ContractEndDate, @CurrentDateTime, @CurrentDateTime)

   -- insert record into credit ledger history table to track
   INSERT INTO dbo.credit_ledger_history(rep_id, contract_id, credit_balance, plan_type, update_type, source, user_id, created_date, last_updated)
   VALUES(@RepId, @ContractId, @CreditBalance, @PlanType, @InsertType, 'System', NULL, @CurrentDateTime, @CurrentDateTime);

   SELECT cl.id, cl.rep_id, cl.sf_contract_id, cl.sf_subscription_product_id, cl.sf_product_id, cl.plan_type,
      cl.credit_balance, cl.contract_start_date, cl.contract_end_date, 
      cl.created_date, cl.last_updated
   FROM @InsertLog cl
END
storedProcedure.name: usp_credit_ledger_insert
